{"article_id":"M9ljSHDXRI6pcCPV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FILE -","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"In this Dec. 2 , 2019 , file photo , Lev Parnas arrives at court in New York .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Parnas , a close associate of President Donald Trump 's personal lawyer , Rudy Giuliani , has provided a trove of text messages and photos to the House committee","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"leading the impeachment inquiry .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"( AP Photo/Seth Wenig , File )","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"FILE -","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"In this Dec. 2 , 2019 , file photo , Lev Parnas arrives at court in New York .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Parnas , a close associate of President Donald Trump 's personal lawyer , Rudy Giuliani , has provided a trove of text messages and photos to the House committee","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"leading the impeachment inquiry .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"( AP Photo/Seth Wenig , File )","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"WASHINGTON","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"( AP ) -","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"House Democrats have released a trove of documents","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"they obtained from Lev Parnas , a close associate of President Donald Trump ' s personal lawyer Rudy Giuliani ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"including a handwritten note","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that mentions","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"asking Ukraine ' s president to investigate \" the Biden case . \"","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"The documents ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"obtained as part of the impeachment investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"show","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Parnas communicating with Giuliani before the removal of Marie Yovanovitch ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"who was the U.S. ambassador to Ukraine .","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"A man","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"named Robert F. Hyde","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"disparaged Yovanovitch in messages to Parnas","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"and gave him updates on her location and cell phone use ,","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"raising questions about possible surveillance .","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"Democrats released the files Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"as they prepared to send articles of impeachment to the Senate for Trump ' s trial .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The documents add new context to their charges","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that Trump pressured Ukraine to investigate Democrats","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"as he withheld military aid .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Parnas was in frequent communication with Giuliani and with Ukrainian officials ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"the messages show .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"He appeared to be pushing unsubstantiated allegations","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that Democrat Joe Biden and his son , Hunter Biden , were somehow engaged in corruption in Ukraine .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Among the documents is a screenshot of a previously undisclosed letter from Giuliani to Ukrainian President Volodymir Zelenskiy","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"dated May 10 , 2019 ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"which was before Zelenskiy took office .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"In the letter , Giuliani requests a meeting with Zelenskiy \" as personal counsel to President Trump and with his knowledge and consent. \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"In the letter , Giuliani said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"he would be accompanied at the meeting by Victoria Toensing , a Washington attorney and Trump ally .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"One of the documents is a handwritten note on stationery from the Ritz-Carlton Hotel in Vienna","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that says","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"\" get Zalensky to Annonce","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that the Biden case will be Investigated. \"","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Trump asked Zelenskiy in a July call to investigate his political rival , Democrat Joe Biden , and his son Hunter .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Hunter Biden served on the board of a gas company","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"based in Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Democrats said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that Parnas ' attorney confirmed","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that Parnas wrote the notes .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The documents","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"- including phone records , texts and flash drives","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"turned over by Parnas -","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"were sent to the House Judiciary Committee by three other House panels","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"\" to be included as part of the official record","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that will be transmitted to the Senate along with the Articles of Impeachment , \"","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"according to a statement .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Some of the materials were made public","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"while others were marked as sensitive .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Parnas and his business partner , Igor Fruman , both U.S. citizens","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"who emigrated from the former Soviet bloc ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"were indicted last year on charges of conspiracy , making false statements and falsification of records .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Prosecutors allege","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"they made outsize campaign donations to Republican causes","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"after receiving millions of dollars","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"originating from Russia .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"The men have pleaded not guilty .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"In several of the documents , Parnas communicated with Giuliani about the removal of Yovanovitch .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"The ambassador ' s ouster ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"ordered by Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"was at the center of the Democrats ' impeachment inquiry .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Yovanovitch testified in the House impeachment hearings","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that she was the victim of a \" smear campaign . \"","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Trump on a July 25 call had promised Zelenskiy","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that Yovanovitch was \" going to go through some things. \"","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Roughly two months earlier , she was recalled from her diplomatic post .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"On April 23 ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"just before Yovanovitch was directed to return to the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Giuliani texted Parnas ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"\" He fired her again. \"","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Parnas texted back ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" I pray","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"it happens this time","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"I ' ll call you tomorrow my brother . \"","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Parnas also received messages from Hyde ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"who referred to Yovanovitch as a \" bitch. \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Hyde is now running for a U.S. House seat in Connecticut .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"After texting about the ambassador ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Hyde gave Parnas detailed updates","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"that suggested","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"he was watching her .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"In one text , Hyde wrote :","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"\" She ' s talked to three people .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"Her phone is off .","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"Her computer is off. \"","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"He said","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"she was under heavy security","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"and \" we have a person inside . \"","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"Hyde at one point texted Parnas","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"that ''they are willing to help","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"if we/you would like a price , \"","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"and \" guess","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"you can do anything in Ukraine with money ...","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"is what I was told . \"","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"Lawrence Robbins , an attorney for Yovanovitch , called for an investigation in to the messages .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"\" Needless to say , the notion","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"that American citizens and others were monitoring Ambassador Yovanovitch ' s movements for unknown purposes","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"is disturbing .","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"We trust","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"that the appropriate authorities will conduct an investigation","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"to determine what happened . \"","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"On Twitter , Hyde dismissed the claims as \" laughable \"","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and appeared to try to distance himself from Parnas .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"he would \" welcome \" an investigation .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"The text messages show","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"that Parnas consulted Giuliani in Jan. 2019","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"after the U.S. denied a visa for former Ukrainian Prosecutor General Viktor Shokin .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Giuliani replied :","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"\" I can revive it . \"","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"The following day , Giuliani told Parnas :","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"\" It ' s going to work","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"I have no 1 in it. \"","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Giuliani then predicted","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"\" he will get one \"","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"before giving Parnas the phone number for Jay Sekulow , the leader of the president ' s personal legal team .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"Sekulow is expected to be part of Trump ' s legal team during the impeachment trial .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"A federal judge earlier this month ruled","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"that Parnas could provide the materials to Congress as part of the impeachment proceedings .","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"Democrats voted in December to impeach Trump for abuse of power and for obstruction of Congress .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":263,"left":141,"right":262,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":136,"right":140,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":135,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":133,"right":134,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":137,"right":139,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":139,"left":138,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":247,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":142,"right":246,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":178,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":165,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":161,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":156,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":146,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":143,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":14,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":147,"right":154,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"le